    "asOf": "2023-01-31",
    "date": "2023-06-02T19:43:55Z",
    "text": "Drone Act of 2023\n\nThis bill creates a federal statutory framework to criminalize various conduct involving the misuse of drones.\n\nAmong its provisions, the bill generally prohibits the\n\n operation of a drone that poses an imminent safety hazard to vessels or motor vehicles; weaponization of a drone (e.g., attaching a firearm or explosive); and operation of a drone that interferes with a law enforcement, emergency response, or military operation or activity of the federal government or of a state, local, or tribal government."
